name: Fast Food v1.0.6
description:
Fast food is a small project made by me  just for fun and it actually got popular on scratch so I decided to add it to itch.io.

Can you beat the high score and be the fastest shopper around? Test your skills in Fast Food where your goal is to get as much food as you can before the time runs out.

This is only v1.0.6 so it doesn't have much but it will have more soon.
